{"tid":450289,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［懷舊］有無巴打去咗睇李彩華演唱會？？？","createTime":"2017-10-28T04:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T13:53:56.000Z","uid":56716,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4817e0b59b767e963887ab00aad010eaedd92636","tid":450289,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T04:51:24.000Z","msg":"李彩華（Rain）今晚喺旺角麥花臣開演唱會喇，繼開場一襲紅裙之後，Rain 換咗黑閃透視裙上陣，勁騷事業線又風騷扭籮，舞姿幾誘人，然後又腳踏dancer唱《熱咖啡》、《最後一夜》、《擋不住的風情》，同女dancers跳完辣身舞，ending仲擺 pose 作狀咀嘴。<br />\n<br />\nRain之後同嘉賓洪杰合唱《意猶未盡》，洪杰又自己唱咗《有借有還》，然後Rain就換咗個懷舊look，唱出連串梅艷芳、張國榮金曲，包括《壞女孩》、《少女心事》、《夢伴》、《Monica》、《H2O》等等。之後Rain再邀請咗《黃金戰士》原唱者胡渭康出場。<br />\n<br />\n當Rain唱完《愛是不保留》後，突然好感觸，喊住話：「好多謝，感謝人生低谷時，好多朋友，屋企人喺我身邊，帶我去認識主，弟兄姊妹牧帥都好愛我，今日好多都嚟咗，感恩多謝大家對我愛，送咗《愛是不保留》俾大家，希望身邊人都送呢首歌俾身邊愛你或不愛你嘅人聽，因為主會愛你同你敵人，希望大家愛身邊每一個人。」<br />\n<br />\n唱咗約22首歌之後，Rain終於唱番自己嘅歌，螢幕就播出以前佢拍過嘅MV，其中一首《愛一個人原來不易》，就見到同古天樂合作嘅畫面。至於壓軸嘅歌，梗係好多人嘅飲歌《你唔愛我啦》，介紹呢首歌時，Rain又忍唔喊話：「感謝在坐所有愛我朋友留到最後一刻，多年開心咁多人錫我，雖然咁多年自己啲歌冇乜點pub過，都得到你哋喜愛。」最後佢高呼今晚好開心，冇法逐一回饋，但內心深處好感謝大家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20171028/57386676\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171028%2F57386676&d=vQchrYGWX0r%2FX%2BesbwO49O9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=ecbe3ce4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171028%2F57386676&h=ee3ad0f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20171028/57386676</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">造型已經老土，仲要唱廿幾首80年代嘅歌，有無巴打真金白銀比錢買飛去睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"21619cd3ed0da476856dd9df96f71da56bebc738","tid":450289,"uid":10504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T04:55:33.000Z","msg":"睇字都睇到起曬雞皮<br />\n柒味濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4bdeda129a2ec1d49058dde57277035a9c45819","tid":450289,"uid":56716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T04:59:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇字都睇到起曬雞皮<br />\n柒味濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想像下有人真心鍾意李彩華啲歌，比錢入去聽佢唱熱咖啡同monica會係咩心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9833dd4bbc977f6da8d0adf2fd599083df197d8","tid":450289,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:00:47.000Z","msg":"有無請&quot;李彩華白色小背心&quot;做嘉賓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49db0c56bbb2606e9d6d11ca889d3ed86693dffd","tid":450289,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:15:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無請&quot;李彩華白色小背心&quot;做嘉賓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梗係有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171027&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=57386330 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171027%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D57386330%20&d=vQchrYGWX0r%2FX%2BesbwO49O9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=f9b5bd31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171027%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D57386330%20&h=12a77639\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171027&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=57386330 </a>"},{"pid":"b68efe81b09ed340e18fb891ac275f16ffe78ea4","tid":450289,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T16:55:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">you dont love me AHHHHHHHHHHHHH</span>"},{"pid":"f7be70bc884d2544570bba2d5b67f6fe4788ce